```python
import param
import panel as pn

patients = config.patients
sessions = config.sessions
patient_ids = []
for patient in patients:
    patient_ids.append(patient['patient_id'])
session_nrs = [1]
    
class PlotterContWatch(param.Parameterized):

    patient_id = param.ObjectSelector(default=60, objects=patient_ids)
    session_nr = param.ObjectSelector(default=1, objects=session_nrs)

    @param.depends('patient_id', 'session_nr')
    def load_symbol(self):
        return hv.Curve(get_pts_of_patient(self.patient_id, self.session_nr), label="Play Time of Movie").opts(framewise=True, width=800, xlabel="time", ylabel="movie frames")
    
```


```python
p = PlotterContWatch()
```


```python
pts_dmap = hv.DynamicMap(p.load_symbol)
```


```python
pn.Column(pn.Row(pn.panel(p.param, parameters=['patient_id', 'session_nr'])), pts_dmap).servable()
```
